title: Kidou Senshi Gundam: Silhouette Formula 91
original_name: 機動戦士ガンダム シルエットフォーミュラ 91
sinopse: In early UC.0123, an Anaheim Electronics team doing testing in the Zebra Zone encounters Crossbone Vanguard's elite Dark Tiger force. The ensuing battle also draws the EFF battleship Ajax and remnants of the Neo Zeon army into the conflict.
